絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4db8c8ca5bf1cde1bcbee8cf8127a1ecf034268d","tid":1543051,"uid":88982,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"樓豬著得le種皮鞋 我估計唔係倫敦金融才俊就係保險精英<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd3281c03f36484543a124eeb68a37511f5c42f","tid":1543051,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"撤回唔係為咗俾香港人降溫；<br />\n撤回係要分化外國政客、媒體，<br />\n令佢地失去插手香港局面既意慾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izm7G7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fizm7G7f.jpg&h=6080f594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https